<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 08:09:08 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>塔利班称巴基斯坦在阿富汗的两次空袭造成八人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/taliban-says-eight-killed-in-pakistans-two-air-strikes-in-afghanistan/articleshow/108581602.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108581602.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塔利班声称巴基斯坦对阿富汗领土的空袭造成平民死亡。巴基斯坦否认，并将袭击归咎于阿富汗领土。双方互相指责，紧张局势加剧。阿富汗塔利班否认允许武装分子使用其领土。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/taliban-says-eight-killed-in-pakistans-two-air-strikes-in-afghanistan/articleshow/108581602.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京谈美国民主：“全世界都在笑”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-on-us-democracy-the-whole-world-is-laughing/articleshow/108580920.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108580920.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;普京批评美国大选，取得破纪录的胜利。西方领导人谴责这次选举。普京警告第三次世界大战。他建议建立一个缓冲区，将俄罗斯的控制范围扩大到乌克兰领土。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:27:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-on-us-democracy-the-whole-world-is-laughing/articleshow/108580920.cms</guid></item><item><title>喀布尔称，巴基斯坦空袭在阿富汗边境地区造成八人死亡，其中包括儿童</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pakistan-air-strikes-kill-eight-including-children-in-afghan-border-areas-says-kabul/articleshow/108580645.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108580645.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;塔利班政府发言人表示，巴基斯坦周一对阿富汗边境地区进行的空袭造成八人死亡，其中包括三名儿童，她强烈谴责这一事件。据发言人扎比胡拉·穆贾希德 (Zabihullah Mujahid) 称，“凌晨 3:00 左右（格林威治标准时间 2230），巴基斯坦飞机轰炸了巴基斯坦边境附近霍斯特和帕克蒂卡地区的平民住宅”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:21:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/pakistan-air-strikes-kill-eight-including-children-in-afghan-border-areas-says-kabul/articleshow/108580645.cms</guid></item><item><title>唐纳德·特朗普评价泽伦斯基：“他是一个比我更好的推销员”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-on-zelenskyy-he-is-a-much-better-salesman-than-me/articleshow/108580912.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108580912.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;前总统特朗普赞扬泽连斯基的筹款技巧，建议向乌克兰提供贷款，批评北约国家，并支持拜登的援助计划。在俄罗斯与乌克兰的冲突中，美国向乌克兰提供了大量援助。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 07:22:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/donald-trump-on-zelenskyy-he-is-a-much-better-salesman-than-me/articleshow/108580912.cms</guid></item><item><title>外交部长会见新西兰外长开启外交之旅</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-foreign-minister-meets-new-zealand-counterpart-to-start-diplomatic-tour/articleshow/108576410.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108576410.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国外交部长王毅访问新西兰和澳大利亚，以加强伙伴关系、解决贸易关税问题，并讨论华为的角色和 Covid-19 大流行调查等敏感问题。王毅的访问标志着促进和平、稳定和繁荣的努力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 05:04:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/chinese-foreign-minister-meets-new-zealand-counterpart-to-start-diplomatic-tour/articleshow/108576410.cms</guid></item><item><title>凯特·米德尔顿可能会就“健康问题”向公众发表讲话：报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-middleton-likely-to-address-public-over-health-concerns-report/articleshow/108575825.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108575825.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;凯特·米德尔顿，也被称为威尔士王妃，预计将在即将举行的公开活动中讨论她的康复情况，因为人们对她缺席的猜测不断。解决她的健康问题的决定取决于凯瑟琳，她强调孩子们的隐私和正常生活。公众对她的最新健康状况的期待与日俱增。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 04:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/kate-middleton-likely-to-address-public-over-health-concerns-report/articleshow/108575825.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚外交部长黄英贤 (Penny Wong) 与索菲·阿卢阿什 (Sophie Allouache) 结婚</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-foreign-minister-penny-wong-marries-sophie-allouache/articleshow/108574142.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108574142.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 04:44:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-foreign-minister-penny-wong-marries-sophie-allouache/articleshow/108574142.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾专家警告称，中国声称对金门海域拥有控制权</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-asserts-control-in-kinmen-waters-taiwanese-experts-warn/articleshow/108575085.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108575085.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据台湾中央通讯社报道，中国在台湾控制的金门附近进行的演习旨在建立控制权。中国海警的入侵引发担忧。专家强调北京的管辖意图，并对灰色地带行动和认知战策略发出警告。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 04:17:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-asserts-control-in-kinmen-waters-taiwanese-experts-warn/articleshow/108575085.cms</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示他在几周后支持堕胎禁令</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-says-he-supports-abortion-ban-after-certain-number-of-weeks/articleshow/108574761.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108574761.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;唐纳德·特朗普周日表示，他赞成在一定周数后实施全国堕胎禁令（例外情况除外），但没有确认具体是多少周，这让他在美国大选的首要问题上的立场变得模糊。特朗普指出，其他地方确实存在几周后堕胎的禁令，特别是在法国和其他欧洲国家。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 04:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/trump-says-he-supports-abortion-ban-after-certain-number-of-weeks/articleshow/108574761.cms</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡在被指控在加沙迷失方向后对美国日益增长的批评进行了反击</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/netanyahu-snaps-back-against-growing-us-criticism-after-being-accused-of-losing-his-way-on-gaza/articleshow/108573304.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108573304.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;内塔尼亚胡抵制美国的批评，否认举行新的选举。对加沙平民死亡人数的担忧依然存在。挑战包括拉法袭击、以色列人质和卡塔尔谈判。加沙的人道主义需求得到强调。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 03:02:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/netanyahu-snaps-back-against-growing-us-criticism-after-being-accused-of-losing-his-way-on-gaza/articleshow/108573304.cms</guid></item><item><title>首架载有逃离海地的美国公民的包机降落在迈阿密</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/first-charter-flight-with-us-citizens-fleeing-haiti-lands-in-miami/articleshow/108573073.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108573073.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;一架载有 30 多名逃离海地帮派暴力的美国公民的包机抵达迈阿密。这架由政府包机的航班降落在迈阿密国际机场。由于骚乱，美国驻太子港大使馆敦促美国公民离开。来自波士顿的乘客阿夫洛特·奎萨（Avlot Quessa）也加入了疏散行动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 02:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/first-charter-flight-with-us-citizens-fleeing-haiti-lands-in-miami/articleshow/108573073.cms</guid></item><item><title>普京：俄北约冲突距离第三次世界大战仅一步之遥</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-russia-nato-conflict-is-just-one-step-from-world-war-3/articleshow/108572633.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108572633.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;普京总统在俄罗斯选举中以创纪录的压倒性优势赢得了后苏联时代的胜利。 1999 年首次掌权的前克格勃中校普京明确表示，选举结果应该向西方传达这样一个信息：无论是在战争还是和平时期，西方领导人都必须面对胆大妄为的俄罗斯。未来几年。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 02:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-russia-nato-conflict-is-just-one-step-from-world-war-3/articleshow/108572633.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列总理称将无视西方，继续推进拉法入侵</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/defying-west-israel-pm-says-will-press-ahead-with-rafah-invasion/articleshow/108571447.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108571447.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 23:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/defying-west-israel-pm-says-will-press-ahead-with-rafah-invasion/articleshow/108571447.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日尔军政府终止美国军事协议，寻求部队撤离</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/niger-junta-ends-us-military-deal-seeks-troops-exit/articleshow/108571593.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108571593.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 00:01:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/niger-junta-ends-us-military-deal-seeks-troops-exit/articleshow/108571593.cms</guid></item><item><title>初步结果显示，普京以创纪录的投票率以压倒性优势赢得俄罗斯大选</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-wins-russia-election-in-landslide-with-record-turnout-early-results-show/articleshow/108569248.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108569248.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;普京在俄罗斯大选中获得压倒性胜利，目标是实现历史性的领导任期。初步结果一出，国际社会就对选举公平性提出批评。纳瓦尔尼的支持者抗议普京的统治，而与乌克兰和西方的紧张关系持续存在。普京赢得了87.8%的选票，这是俄罗斯后苏联历史上的最高得票率。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 19:39:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-wins-russia-election-in-landslide-with-record-turnout-early-results-show/articleshow/108569248.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登：两个选秀权之间，一个是精神不健康，另一个是我</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-between-2-picks-one-mentally-unfit-others-me/articleshow/108569209.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108569209.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总统乔·拜登在华盛顿举行的一次招待会上开玩笑说，有两名候选人获得了本党的提名，并幽默地暗示他就是其中之一。在烤架俱乐部和基金会晚宴上，这种玩笑仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 19:32:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-between-2-picks-one-mentally-unfit-others-me/articleshow/108569209.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯大选初步结果揭晓，普京以88%的得票率领先</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-leads-russia-election-with-88-of-vote-show-early-results/articleshow/108569153.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108569153.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;普京在反对票有限或没有反对票的情况下在选举中获得了 87.9% 的支持率。镇压政治异见。此次选举距离普京在乌克兰发动特别军事行动，引发欧洲最致命的冲突仅两年多。纳瓦尔尼的遗孀在柏林大使馆投票。损坏的选票抗议普京。选举期间严密控制，逮捕了 80 人。据报道，投票站遭到破坏。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 19:14:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/putin-leads-russia-election-with-88-of-vote-show-early-results/articleshow/108569153.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦寻求国际货币基金组织超过80亿美元的更大救助计划</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-to-seek-larger-bailout-package-of-over-8-billion-from-imf/articleshow/108568957.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108568957.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;资金短缺的巴基斯坦将通过扩展基金贷款（EFF）正式向国际货币基金组织（IMF）请求救助计划。有报道称，伊斯兰堡可能会在4月15日至20日于华盛顿特区举行的国际货币基金组织/世界银行春季会议上寻求超过80亿美元的资金。预计巴基斯坦可能会像2008年那样要求增加配额。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 18:47:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-to-seek-larger-bailout-package-of-over-8-billion-from-imf/articleshow/108568957.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦总统扎尔达里：巴基斯坦决心反击一切进入其边境并实施恐怖活动的势力</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-resolves-to-counter-every-force-that-enters-its-border-and-commits-terror-president-zardari/articleshow/108568503.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108568503.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦总统阿西夫·阿里·扎尔达里周日表示，巴基斯坦将对任何进入其边境实施恐怖活动的势力进行报复，并对每名阵亡士兵的鲜血负责。扎尔达里发表此番言论之前，他参加了为两名军官举行的葬礼祈祷活动，这两名军官是周六在恐怖袭击中丧生的七名巴基斯坦陆军人员之一。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 17:46:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-resolves-to-counter-every-force-that-enters-its-border-and-commits-terror-president-zardari/articleshow/108568503.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度、斯里兰卡和马来西亚将设置马尔维群岛选举投票箱</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/ballot-boxes-for-malvides-elections-to-be-placed-in-india-sri-lanka-malaysia/articleshow/108568709.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/108568709.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 18:04:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/ballot-boxes-for-malvides-elections-to-be-placed-in-india-sri-lanka-malaysia/articleshow/108568709.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>